commit.message:
Fix missing DLL

First reported by diogeneswasok
https://github.com/bleachbit/bleachbit/issues/1569

This partially reverses this commit
https://github.com/bleachbit/bleachbit/commit/f0a8f2faf2674ce64e3a12cb90c74cd4d2d652b0
Continue to improve robustness of Wayland check

Fix detection of Wayland

First reported by k1gen
https://github.com/bleachbit/bleachbit/issues/1578

Based on idea of proletarius101 to use environment variable
https://github.com/bleachbit/bleachbit/pull/1577

This should work on FreeBSD, reported by snss806
https://github.com/bleachbit/bleachbit/issues/1589
Bump version to 4.6.1 beta
